{"tid":733062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大隻男機場跑道公園跑步   即興落水游1公里惹墮海驚魂","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T13:45:59.000Z","uid":31314,"like":258,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"56bd6055022480574802416df362c3794235d9ec","tid":733062,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"一名年約40歲、身材壯碩的男子，今日（7日）凌晨2時許，偕數名友人於啟德郵輪碼頭對開跑道公園跑步，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>期間疑一時興致來襲，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">向友人自稱能輕易游至一公里外的觀塘公眾碼頭</span>；事主話音剛落，急不及待脫去上衣躍入水中「大展身手」</strong></span>。附近當值保安員見狀，以為有人墮海遇險報警。<br />\n<br />\n消防船接報趕抵現場，派出蛙人落海救援，未幾於觀塘公眾碼頭尋獲事主，其時他已游至岸邊，並無受傷，由在場人員將他載返啟德郵輪碼頭後拒絕送院。警員向事主警誡一番：「你游水叻都係咁話，要咁多人搵你！」事主聞言亦連聲道歉，向救援人員表示：「唔好意思」，及後由友人陪同離去。"},{"pid":"a822cbe221aec456bfe2d48be0bb503d604535aa","tid":733062,"uid":185165,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"相呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf1bd755c1ea4e04a882544eb3fa005bb064926a","tid":733062,"uid":12823,"like":4,"dislike":31,"score":-27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:33:21.000Z","msg":"弱智廢中"},{"pid":"b23eb8a586bfa8d5267cffc662bcad25ef967fa9","tid":733062,"uid":64345,"like":76,"dislike":108,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180707/photo/bkn-20180707031425318-0707_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180707104849\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180707%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180707031425318-0707_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180707104849&h=91ca5d45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f18e4a69d7a5938bd382ce361325c3b392e09b2f","tid":733062,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"a822cbe221aec456bfe2d48be0bb503d604535aa","tid":733062,"uid":185165,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"相呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"